    Joe Mama
    5.0 out of 5 stars Replacement for old one--love it!
    Reviewed in the United States on 22 June 2023
    Verified Purchase
    I had previously bought this same set when I got my iPhone 11 several years ago. That one wore out (the backing peeled away from the part that goes around the sides, so it was falling off constantly). I loved it so much that I had to purchase it again. It was no longer available from that vendor, so I was glad to see this one. It seems to be exactly the same!
    I've been using it for a few months now, and it's holding up just fine.
    I don't use the neck strap personally, but I love the wrist strap for some extra protection/gripping. On my old one, when the wrist strap gave out (it's just ribbon material), I purchased a separate Disney-themed wrist strap, which I use with this case because it's more durable--in other words, feel free to swap out wrist & neck straps if you don't like the ones it comes with or when they fall apart.
    The only problem I had with the old one (before age took its toll) is that the ring pulled apart from being shoved in my pocket. I swapped it out for a different ring, and again, that's been just fine.
    The slide part on the back works well for sliding your hand under to grip the phone better, and I love it for a stand when I have my phone on its side.
    So...the basic gist here is: I loved it so much I bought it again. (This is actually my 3rd one--I had the same thing for an earlier phone--no issues--I only replaced it when I got a larger phone in the iPhone 11.)
